  "projectType": "general",
  "projectName": "ProxyDroid",
  "projectDescription": "A global proxy app for Android that routes all device traffic through HTTP, SOCKS4, or SOCKS5 proxy servers using iptables NAT rules or a VPN interface, with support for per-app proxying, PAC scripts, NTLM authentication, and network-based auto-connect.",
